The food is good, but the service is what makes this place great.  Every step of the service is impeccable, all the way down to the mini lemon loaf cakes we were given to take home, and the cab that was hailed for us as we left.  The food is perfectly lovely (the duck I had was tasty), but we visited other places where the food was more memorable.  If I could give 3.75 stars, I would
